<div class="bd-example">
  <h3>Claymore Dual Miner</h3>
  <p>
    <code><em>EthDcrMiner64</em> -epool <em>{{config.StratumHost}}</em>:{{config.StratumPort}}<em>-esm 0</em> -ewal <em>0x0</em> -eworker <em>RIG1</em> -allcoins 1 -allpools 1</code>
  </p>
  <p><span class="label label-info">Hint</span> use <code><em>./ethdcrminer64</em></code> under Linux/ubuntu<br />
  </p>
</div>

<div class="bd-example">
  <h3>Ethminer</h3>
  <p>
    <code>ethminer <em>-U</em> -F stratum1+tcp://<em>0x0</em>.<em>RIG1</em>@<em>{{config.StratumHost}}</em>:{{config.StratumPort}}</code>
  </p>
  <p><span class="label label-info">Hint</span> use <code><em>-U</em></code> option for NVIDIA GPU, <code><em>-G</em></code> option for AMD GPU.</p>
</div>
